  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Logistics Manager",
  "description": "<p>As a Logistics Manager, you will oversee and optimize the warehouse and supply chain operations, focusing on efficiency and alignment with business objectives. Collaborating closely with cross-functional teams including logistics, marketing, and sales, you will ensure seamless coordination to meet operational goals and customer requirements.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Strategically plan and manage logistics, warehouse, transportation and customer services.</li>\n  <li>Liaise and negotiate with suppliers, retailers and resolve any arising problems or complaints from customers.</li>\n  <li>Keep track of quality, quantity, stock levels, delivery times, transport costs and efficiency.</li>\n  <li>Optimize transportation routes and modes to minimize lead times and costs, ensuring on-time product delivery.</li>\n  <li>Arrange warehouse, catalog goods, plan routes and process shipments.</li>\n  <li>Implement effective warehouse management practices to streamline stock or inventory handling, storage, and order fulfillment processes for retailers and customers.</li>\n  <li>Able to meet cost, productivity, accuracy and timeliness targets.</li>\n  <li>Monitor market trends, customer demands, industry developments to implement best practices and innovative solutions to enhance supply chain efficiency.</li>\n  <li>Supervise, coach and train warehouse workforce for any issues or challenges that arise.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bachelor's degree in supply chain management, Logistics, Business Administration, or any related field.</li>\n  <li>Minimum of 10 years of working experiences in logistics and supply chain management.</li>\n  <li>Excellent leadership and dynamic team player with the ability to motivate team, foster good relationships and collaboration, therefore achieving great outcomes and results.</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication skills with the ability to build relationships with customers and suppliers.</li>\n  <li>Strong decision-making skills, problem-solving skills.</li>\n  <li>Details-oriented, results-oriented, and good time management skills.</li>\n</ul>",
